content:
{
  "inner": "Where am I? Who is that woman? Why is there a locked door and a wooden box in this room?",
  "speak": "Excuse me, miss. Do you have any idea what's going on here?",
  "action": "I'll stand up and approach the woman slowly, keeping a safe distance between us. As I speak to her, I'll try to assess her demeanor and see if she poses any threat." 
}

{
  "inner": "Okay, she seems to be just as confused as I am. Maybe if we work together, we can figure out what the hell is going on here.",
  "speak": "I don't know what's going on either. But if we work together, maybe we can figure it out.",
  "action": "I'll make sure to maintain a safe distance from the woman as I talk to her. I'll also keep an eye on the door and the wooden box, just in case something strange happens. If the woman seems willing to collaborate, maybe we can start exploring the room for any clues or hidden passages." 
}

{
  "inner": "A key? That's a good start. But what's outside? Why can't we come back? I have so many questions.",
  "speak": "A key! Maybe we can finally unlock that door. But the note is ominous. Any idea what's outside or why we can't come back?",
  "action": "I'll approach the box and take a closer look at the key and the note. I'll inspect the key for any engravings or symbols that might offer a clue as to what it unlocks. I'll also try to catch a glimpse of the woman's expression to see if she knows any more than I do." 
}
